query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind in ('complete','complete+verified','crew') AND (k.keyword like '%investigation%' OR k.keyword like '%battle%') AND (pi.note like '%Sean Boyle%') AND (rt.role like '%Volker Boehm%' OR rt.role like '%HH%') AND it3.info in ('biographical movies','goofs','certificates','studios','tech info','adaption','LD catalog number','where now','other works') AND cct1.kind not in ('complete','cast','complete+verified') AND (chn.name like '%Wonder Woman%' OR chn.name like '%Joker%' OR chn.name like '%John McClane%' OR chn.name like '%Hermione Granger%' OR chn.name like '%Atticus Finch%') AND (cn.name like '%Amblin Partners%' OR cn.name like '%Blumhouse Productions%' OR cn.name like '%Sony Pictures Entertainment%' OR cn.name like '%Amblin Television%' OR cn.name like '%Paramount Pictures%') AND cn.country_code in ('cz','cg','nr','tj') AND (n.name like '%K%' OR n.name like '%q%') AND it.info not in ('LD frequency response','books','LD pressing plant','book','LD release date','gross','LD group genre','LD audio quality','LD laserdisc title','LD subtitles','LD quality program','LD category','LD dialogue intellegibility','trivia') AND (mc.note like '%UK%')
